{"tid":315414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮誤稱習近平「中華民國總統」","createTime":"2017-07-10T04:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T04:36:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e37c3018794f07182e3f84d012b8ffe50c39f78c","tid":315414,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:07:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20084635&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20084635%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170710&d=f%2BQVzLxqOPmwvy0z%2BjW7Lv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=5af08181\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20084635%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170710&h=7a4908d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20084635&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170710</a><br />\n<br />\n白宮誤稱習近平「中華民國總統」<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n特朗普近日對中國約束北韓的進展甚不耐煩，但他前天趁G20峯會與中國國家主席習近平會面期間大展友善，向其變臉稱「我們是好朋友」。然而白宮在講述今次會面時，卻將習近平錯寫成「中華民國總統」。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n特朗普與習近平再度會面。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n特拉攏習：有你作為朋友真榮幸<br />\n<br />\n今次會面為時約一個半小時，是繼習近平4月訪美後，兩人再一次面對面交流。特朗普稱，十分讚賞中國在促進朝鮮半島和平上作出的努力：「有你作為朋友真榮幸，北韓問題的處理，雖比你我預期慢，但最終會成功。」不過他依舊提出中美現行貿易並不公平，要求再次談判。<br />\n習近平則提到，強化中美合作有助維持全球繁榮穩定，雙方之間雖有「敏感議題」，有很多工作仍待推動，但已在相當的範疇取得進展。他亦再表示反對美方在南韓部署「薩德」反導彈系統。<br />\n特朗普重視對華關係，可是白宮在稱呼別國領導人上再次出醜。白宮在兩人會面後發新聞稿，將習近平稱為「中華民國總統」（President Xi of the Republic of China），他們同日較早前也將日本首相安倍晉三誤稱為「日本總統」。一日內犯下兩個嚴重錯誤，成網民恥笑對象。<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n長子　女婿承認密會俄律師<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;6小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n穿英名牌V領連身裙　值7,800元<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;6小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n峯會閉幕　馬克龍：世界從未如此分化<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;6小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n特自誇成功　輿論批無全球領袖風範<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;6小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n非民選顧問　與習近平文翠珊同坐伊萬卡暫代父開G20特朗普被轟如獨裁者<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;6小時前"},{"pid":"115373a509e76a62390add96ad887ba1dc38e283","tid":315414,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b2ed27e514b5be20b106391f66ecb3af17ef9f","tid":315414,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:15:37.000Z","msg":"侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cfecc5e569d21e4e3e9d37ad4e2e90c2d2d8c7","tid":315414,"uid":68916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:21:40.000Z","msg":"簡稱啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb62f267a6f368f081807f58f1e92771bfb3e873","tid":315414,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:30:22.000Z","msg":"CCTVB 好緊張<br />\n成個報導大篇幅講 佢講錯過幾多次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTITLE講錯少事,不過 中華民國 唔會錯囉<br />\n明玩9你支那 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f701dea7f11851ccfbb06c8b775a1e207b89081","tid":315414,"uid":7291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425faf3a1a836e869a8acee32cbdf23aa4b919b2","tid":315414,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:32:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CCTVB 好緊張<br />\n